items.name: chunker_python
items.description: This repository, chunker_python, is a Python-based project designed to perform chunking operations, which involve splitting data into smaller, manageable pieces for processing, storage, or transmission. The project is structured to use pip for dependency management, ensuring that required libraries are easily installed and maintained.
